Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:37.64,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quando pensi a me, sempre
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:44.29,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bisbiglierò
